App-RFC version 0.05
====================

This application is for automatic retrieve RFC by number and display it
under $PAGER program, searching through rfc-index.txt by arbitrary text,
and retrieving (from crontab) rfc index file (and optionally display any
differences between old and new).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Getopt::Long, LWP::UserAgent, HTTP::Date, HTTP::Headers.

